<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Training Simulator - Login</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/style.css">
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Background Image with Overlay -->
    <div class="bg-image"></div>
    <div class="bg-overlay"></div>

    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="navbar-container">
            <div class="logo">
                <h1><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Training Simulator</h1>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Navigation Links -->
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <li class="nav-item active">
                    <a href="index.html" class="nav-links">Home</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="main-content">
        <!-- Login Container -->
        <div class="login-container">
            <div class="login-header">
                <h2>Welcome Back!</h2>
                <p>Sign in to access your training dashboard</p>
            </div>
            <form id="loginForm">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                    <div class="input-with-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                        <input type="email" id="email" required placeholder="Enter your email">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password">Password</label>
                    <div class="input-with-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                        <input type="password" id="password" required placeholder="Enter your password">
                        <i class="fas fa-eye toggle-password" id="togglePassword"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="login-btn">
                    <span>Login</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
                </button>
            </form>
            <p id="loginMessage" class="message"></p>
            <div class="login-footer">
                <a href="#" id="forgotPassword">Forgot password?</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Commercial Slider -->
        <div class="commercial-slider">
            <div class="slider-container">
                <div class="slide active" id="mission-vision-slide">
                    <div class="slide-content">
                        <h3> About our Company</h3>
                        <p>
                                At Delacruz Network Solutions, we are a leading provider of high-speed, reliable wireless internet services, committed to bringing fast, affordable, and accessible internet to homes and businesses across the region. As a proud Wireless Internet Service Provider (WISP), we leverage cutting-edge technology to offer seamless connectivity, no matter the location. Whether you're in a bustling city or a remote rural area, our services are designed to ensure that you stay connected when you need it most.
                                
                                We take pride in providing a service that not only meets the needs of today but anticipates the demands of tomorrow. Our team is dedicated to ensuring that every customer receives top-tier support and technology, ensuring an uninterrupted experience, wherever you are.
                                </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Features Slide -->
                <div class="slide" id="features-slide">
                    <div class="slide-content">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Key Features</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Realistic technical simulations</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Progress tracking & analytics</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Certification programs</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Expert-led training modules</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Testimonials Slide -->
                <div class="slide" id="testimonials-slide">
                    <div class="slide-content">
                        <div class="testimonial"> 
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Our Mission</h3>
                        <p>Our mission is to bridge the digital divide by providing reliable, fast, and affordable wireless internet to underserved and urban communities alike. We aim to empower individuals, businesses, and communities by enabling them to connect, learn, and grow with the power of the internet.

                            We are committed to innovation, customer satisfaction, and the ongoing development of our network infrastructure to ensure the highest levels of service. Our goal is to not only be a provider of internet access but a partner in the digital transformation of the communities we serve.</p>
                        <div class="separator"></div>
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Our Vision</h3>
                        <p>To be the most trusted and innovative Wireless Internet Service Provider, delivering unmatched connectivity solutions that empower individuals and businesses. We envision a future where every person, regardless of location, has access to reliable, high-speed internet, enabling them to fully engage in the digital world.
                        </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Slider Controls -->
            <div class="slider-controls">
                <button class="control-btn prev-btn"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i></button>
                <div class="slider-dots">
                    <span class="dot active" data-slide="0"></span>
                    <span class="dot" data-slide="1"></span>
                    <span class="dot" data-slide="2"></span>
                </div>
                <button class="control-btn next-btn"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p content-center>&copy; 2025 Training Simulator. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
    

    <script type="module" src="assets/scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
</body>
</html>